Description: Use reservation and restaurant visit data from
    Recruit Holding to predict the number of visitors to a restaurant for
    future dates. This package contains all the necessary work to perform
    the prediction :exploratory data analysis, prediction model using
    xgboost and results visualized with our shinyapp.
